A bundle that allows you to read and write RESTful resources in YAML.

Requires Ruby, ActiveSupport and ActiveResource.

Adds bundle commands: restmate.show, restmate.build, restmate.create and restmate.update<tab>.

Configuration:

Edit config.yml in <BUNDLE>/Support/config.yml to include the resource, the base url, and a whitelist of attributes that you want to edit:

model: Post
url: http://www.blog.com
whitelist:
  - id
  - body
  - title
  - published